{"tid":2174580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"ScienceDirect研究，低劑量HCQ對武肺有效及降低死亡率","createTime":"2020-08-26T03:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T07:14:10.000Z","uid":294518,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0cef8ca00410553b818c8cd12b88f68a89783be7","tid":2174580,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"與僅支持治療相比，低劑量HCQ單一療法與在症狀發作早期或之後診斷和治療的COVID-19住院患者的死亡率較低獨立相關。<br />\nConclusions<br />\nCompared to supportive care only, low-dose HCQ monotherapy was independently associated with lower mortality in hospitalized patients with COVID-19 diagnosed and treated early or later after symptom onset.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZaYUuCk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZaYUuCk.png&h=dcbf7213&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/08/26/112321_0b49ddc6aada8b1e7aae4e6478d5845f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F08%2F26%2F112321_0b49ddc6aada8b1e7aae4e6478d5845f.png&h=28f9aef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0924857920303423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0924857920303423&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=36e213ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0924857920303423</a>"},{"pid":"ce59ef1956f4a40a50b3cc4d234567d018260ecc","tid":2174580,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"HCQ = ?"},{"pid":"b0c6fd86dd955bd082f5981d53486431a99310eb","tid":2174580,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26bc1fe088e8ba2e3db8fca710b2a139ecb6d272","tid":2174580,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce59ef1956f4a40a50b3cc